<li><a href="http://eternalzttz.com/hexo-next.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">eternalzttz</a></li>
<li><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo.io</a></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
